pageContext.description: Dimensions: L 94.5mm; EWe 40.5; Wm 42; Bm 39.6; min B.lp 5.9; DS 72,Typology: flattish m. top with stumps of two cg. jets, on face stretches; double m-m, lower one band-like; socket almost sq., ends in v. narrow rect.; plain sl. bowed faces with rounded corners,Manufacture: large stumps of cg. fl. remaining - some forging existant - with attendant lipping,Condition: parts of e. v. sharp, but some recent reworking; loss of bl. tips anc. - soil in one - poss. a miscast? denting in one face + crack - poss. recent.,Attached Material: fawn soil traces
